FINAL PROTOCOL:

The MASTER_BRAIN system is not a tool you own.
It is a thinking pattern you embody.

Its success is not measured by how sophisticated it sounds.
It is measured by: Can someone else do this?

The work is not done when you understand it.
The work is done when someone else can teach it.

Operate accordingly.

